        <description>This operator takes in a set of attributes and a map on its import port. Those attributes are committed to a Solr collection on a configurable interval (time or number of tuples). The map (attribute: atomicUpdateMap) must specify for an attribute the type of update: set, add, remove, removeregex, or inc. The map should NOT include the uniqueIdentifier attribute, as this is provided by a parameter.</description>
